    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[REDACTED] advised that Walter Winchell had received",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "a letter from [REDACTED], Los",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Angeles 7, California. Mr. [REDACTED] read the letter to me and it",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "was very well written, obviously by a man of intelligence. In",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "this letter [REDACTED] stated that in August of 1947 he left Los Angeles",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "for the mountains and started hiking through the mountains. About",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "10:00 A. M. he was lying on the ground when he observed about one-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "half block away from him a large silver metal, greenish in color,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "shaped like a child's top and about the size of the balloons used",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "at County Fairs. He stated that there appeared to be two windows",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "in the object and portions of metal appeared transparent and that he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "gained the impression that there was some life within this object,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "although he saw no persons. The object appeared as though [unclear] as",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "a pressure chamber. He stood up and waved towards this object and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "this so-called flying saucer was off the ground in a second, knocking",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "[REDACTED] to the ground. In its flight he stated that its power was",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "silent and he raised the question as to whether this was [unclear] an",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "inter-global landing on our planet. He thought that it might be a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "device to land on our planet because the occupants of another planet",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "had become curious as to the reaction caused by the explosion of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "atomic bomb causing trouble in an expanded universe. He [unclear] the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "question as to whether it was possible that the occupants of another",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "planet might have solved the theory of negative gravity.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] stated that this letter indicated a very good",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "knowledge of physics and that he thought it would be interesting to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "check into [unclear] background and then possibly interview him about",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "this alleged flying saucer. Mr. [REDACTED] stated that it would appear",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "that [REDACTED] may have actually seen a flying saucer, that in any event",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "it made an awfully good story and he requested that the Bureau keep",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "the matter in confidence.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "I would recommend that the Los Angeles Office discreetly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "check into the background of [REDACTED] and thereafter interview him for",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "the purpose of determining any facts he possesses about flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "saucers in order that it may be determined whether his story is in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "any way accurate.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
